name: Divine Arsenal G-4
effect: If you control no monsters, or you control a "Divine Arsenal" monster, you can Special Summon this card (from your hand or GY). You can only Special Summon "Divine Arsenal G-4" once per turn this way. If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can Special Summon 1 LIGHT Machine monster from your Deck. You can only use this effect of "Divine Arsenal G-4" once per turn. You cannot Special Summon monsters the turn you activate this effect, except Machine monsters.
